Product name: Mid-Century Jewelry Modernist Necklace Earring Set Ed Levin Jewelry Sterling and 14k Gold Necklace & Earring Set Mother's Day Gifts For Her
Description:
This Ed Levin necklace & earring set is a perfect example of his flawless and stunning sense of design. 
For the discerning collector of mid-20th century jewelry or a truely lovely gift, I offer this  wonderful early mid-century set of Sterling Silver & 14K Gold Shadow Box earrings and necklace by the renown Ed Levin. 
These fantastic pieces are in excellent condition and would make a truly remarkable Gift to be cherished and past down through generations. 
Known for his fluid designs, these are just a perfect example of his early works.  So simple but elegant; a must have for those of you who appreciate the famous designers of this era. 
They are stamped Sterling and have the Ed Levin hallmark in script.  The necklace is done in the shadow box design. The top oval is a brushed sterling silver; the bottom oval is 14K gold over sterling silver and the suspended ball in the middle is solid 14K gold. 
The necklace is 18" long and the pendant is 1" tall and almost 1/2 wide. The earrings are the same size. The total weight is 9.6g.
Ed Levin passed away February 23, 2008. In a Tribute article in Modern Silver magazine, Nancy E Schindler said " Levin's work has always had the uncanny ability to look flawless and modern in design while maintaining an elegant simplicity. Good jewelry design doesn't need to be complicated. In fact, the very best of modern jewelry design is able to convey a sense of monumentality while being sneakily simple and unexpectedly comfortable. Ed Levin's work has possessed those qualities since the 1950's when he began his role as a pioneer in modern jewelry design."
The satisfaction of my customers is extremely important to me. I search for vintage jewelry of impeccable quality and rarity. I only offer the best I can find. No Dealers please. 
I urge you to read all my shop policies prior to purchase and carefully look at all pictures.  I want you to feel confident involving any transactions with me and welcome any questions you might have. Also please read my shop reviews to see what others say about me and my shop.
Serious and reasonable offers will be considered, just ask ; )
All jewelry and Men’s accessories are sent in a jewelry box with  ribbon & bow and ready for gifting.

Product name: Vintage PFAFF 130 Sewing Machine
Description:
This vintage PFAFF 130 sewing machine has just been cleaned and serviced. It is running like new! Made in Germany, these machines are known for their quality construction. 
This machine was purchased new in 1953 and has had one owner. The motor and belt were replaced several years ago. I have the original PFAFF motor and will include it with purchase if desired.
Comes with several genuine PFAFF attachments, the bobbin case, and the original metal PFAFF storage box. Also included are the power cord with foot control, operating manual, a few PFAFF needles. 
The original carrying case is in great vintage condition. It had a broken handle, which has been replaced with a new custom made leather handle. The snap closures work perfectly.
This heavy duty PFAFF machine weighs approx. 44lbs., so shipping costs will reflect the weight.
Message me if additional information or photos are needed. Always glad to oblige.

Product name: 13,7" UNIQUE Astronomical Wall Clock PERSONALIZED  - Luxury Gift  Wall Clock, Wedding Gift, Retirement,Anniversary Gift
Description:
This astronomical clock is unique in the world and it not only makes a great time piece but it is also a luxury gift suitable for offices, homes and any other spaces. The astronomical clock is a hybrid product wood and electronic mechanism. Designed and manufactured in Romania, this is a patented mechanism.
This clock is actually an horology system with 7 functions: am/pm, week days, moon phases, zodiac signs, seasons and month.  All the mechanism are in plain sigh,. visible and the whole image  is that of a mechanism moving different sized wheels.
 It has a retro , punk-steamed look thanks to the innovatory technique used to make this clock.
This clock is called Astronomic as it shows not only the time (AM/PM), but also the days of the week, moon phases, date, zodiac signs, seasons and month.
** The clock comes in a wooden box that can be PERSONALIZED for an extra 15 dollars. The clock can also be personalized with the name of the person"s receiving this gift or with the company logo.
How does it work?
When the owner starts the timer and installs it, all the wooden wheels of the mechanism work together and move one another in a complex mechanism showing the time, date, month, etc.
Astronomical wood clock, manually assembled. 
Indicates: 
- hour; 
- minute; 
- month; 
- day of the week; 
- date; 
- AM/PM; 
- season; 
- moon phases.
TECHNICAL DATA
Wood structure, laser-crafted
Outer diameter: 35 cm/ 13,7 inches
Quartz-based mechanism
Weight ~ 300 grams
Photoluminiscent digit
USAGE specifications:
Optimal temperature for functioning – 16-28 degrees Celsius – 60,8 - 82,4 Fahrenheit
Avoid exposure to moisture and  direct sunlight
Use only alkaline batteries AA (not included)
The motor mechanism is electronic, based on quartz, long lasting and very accurate
PERSONALIZE your clock:
The clock , but also the the box can be personalized with a name or a company logo.
The personalizing is done by laser engraving.
Please specify the name as you would like it to appear on the clock (Ex. "SMITH" or "SMITHS") and date established (for example: date of marriage) you would like on the clock in the notes to seller section. 
You can add this option for an additional €10 for the clock and €15 for the box. 
 If you would like your clock personalized with a family name, established date or company logo, please contact us.
SHIPPING:
IT IS NOT INCLUDED
Ready to ship in 3-5 working days (if a personalized order please take into consideration another day)
INTERNATIONAL CUSTOMERS please be aware that you are responsible for all import fees, duties, VAT, GST/PST, taxes, etc. and this is not included in my prices. There is no way for me to know what, if any, the fees could be for every item in every country. I hope you understand! 
Please see Shipping & Policies to calculate shipping cost.
Warranty: 24 months.
Made in Romania.
This Astronomical wall clock is more than a wall clock. It's a refined and tasteful gift  that elegantly enriches any home, office or council board rooms.
With a spectacular design and refined  look, this clock will be a very appreciate gift.

What is Black Seed Oil?
Black Seed Oil Health Benefits
Black seed oil is an oil derived by pressing the seeds of the Nigella Sativa plant. 
The seeds are also commonly referred to as black cumin. The nutrient-rich oil of 
black seed has been used for hundreds of years in the Middle East and South Asia 
as a natural remedy for a variety of ailments
.
What are the Benefits of Black Seed Oil?
Studies have shown that black seed oil is an effective anti-oxidant, anti-bacterial, and anti-inflammatory remedy. As a result, it is often used to fight infections and strengthen the immune system, which is suitable for treating the following conditions:
headaches
toothaches
nasal congestion
colds and flu
digestive and gastrointestinal problems
hair and skin problems
allergies
diabetes

Product name: Solar System Planets Cross Stitch Patterns - Set of 9 - PDF Instant Download
Description:
Have some fun stitching all 8 planets in our solar system (with Pluto thrown in as a bonus)! 
This instant download is one PDF that includes:
        - a photograph of each finished planet

        - a DMC thread color key for each planet

Full specifications:

        - For best results, stitch each planet with two strands of floss

The planets are all slightly different sizes to very roughly represent the actual sizes of the planets in relation to one another.
